          />
        </div>
        <div class="kiwi-body">
          <span class="kiwi-category">Gender Diverse Health Organisation</span>
          <h3>PATHA</h3>
          <p>
            The Professional Association for Transgender Health Aotearoa is an
            interdisciplinary professional organisation working to promote the
            health, wellbeing and rights of transgender people.
          </p>
